summary:
A Little Bit Like Fate | One-Shot | Teen&Up | 7.7k “So,” Harry starts. “Since I heard you and
your friend are not getting...
caption:
A Little Bit Like Fate | One-Shot | Teen&Up | 7.7k

“So,” Harry starts. “Since I heard you and your friend are not getting married, uhm… Would it be appropriate to ask you to stay for the kiss-in?”

“Really?” Louis says, light and playful. “And who would I be kissing?” He looks up and offers a sweet smile, perfectly innocent.

“Oh, I don’t know.” Harry is playing along, keeping his tone airy, but he takes a step forward and smirks. “With those cheekbones, I think you could kiss whoever you wanted.”

Or:

Louis stumbles upon a kiss-in protest for LGBTQ rights, and he meets Harry. They click. It feels a little bit like fate.

I’ll See You There💋Harry Styles💋Part 12
HARRY’S P.O.V
“Hold on, Love.” Before we headed out I grabbed my car keys, wallet and...
body:
I’ll See You There💋Harry Styles💋Part 12

HARRY’S P.O.V

“Hold on, Love.” Before we headed out I grabbed my car keys, wallet and thought about what I was forgetting about but I couldn’t think of anything so I just grabbed Y/N’s hand and walked out the door. 

“So here’s the plan, Niall warned me there’s paparazzi in the front, so here are my car keys go through the back, down the stairs and drive the car to the front of the hotel and wait for me and Niall. Don’t forget to put the shades and hat on so they don’t see your face.” I kissed her and give her my car keys and I head towards the elevator. The doors open and I step in and click 1⭐️ and take my phone to out texting Niall, “How’s it looking?” He texted back, “More and more showing up.” I text back, “Fuck, okay Y/N is getting the car and I’m coming down.” I put my phone in my pocket and looked up as the doors open and I step out heading to the check in desk. “Hi Mr.Styles how can I help you” said the lady siting at the desk, “I want to check out.” “Okay…*She checks out Harry*..okay sir you’re all set, thank you so much for spending time at our hotel have a great day.” I smiled and nodded, “You as well”

Y/N’s P.O.V

As Harry enters the elevator I go back in the room and grabs my things and my phone, leaves the room and heads to the back stairs. I rush down the stairs and gets to level 1 and goes the parking lot and looks for Harry’s car, “fuck where is it…where where..AhH!” Runs as fast as I can to his car and unlocks it and gets in and starts the engine, “what am I doing? I barely know him but I feel like I’ll do anything for him..” I look at the mirror, “I’ve known this man for only like 2 days, he keeps buying me things and..oh what am I doing” starts driving and as I turn the corner I see a whole lot of flash going on and a bunch of paparazzi.

NIALL’S P.O.V

“HARRY!!” I waved at him and watch him walk away from the desk and towards me, “Where’s the girl?” “Her name is Y/N and she went around the back to get the car” “Good idea” I looked away from harry from looked at the doors and sighed as I said, “you ready for this” he nods and we walk towards the door as we see flashing lights. “I think that’s her” “Yeah it is let’s go” We push through the crowd and opens the car door and gets in and as we close the close we start laughing.

Y/N’s P.O.V

I put the hat on and the hair on my face and starts pressing the horn so they would move out the way, I see Harry and Niall and they start pushing through the crowd and gets in the car and I try to get people to move out the way and then finally I drove off. The boys start laughing and I smirk shaking my head “You can take the hat off now love” I take my hat off and pushes my hair back and out of my face. “Where am I driving to boys?” “Let’s go to my flat” Harry nods, “Let’s get something to eat first” “alright, but Y/N let me drive just pull over and switch seats” I pull over and hop out as did Niall and I get in the bank with Harry as I close the door he pulls me close to him and puts his arm around my shoulder.

Harry’s P.O.V

Niall pulled up to our favorite restaurant and we got out as Y/N was getting out, “Love I think it’s best you stay in the car don’t want people ambushing you, me and Nialler will be back in a few minutes.” She nods and closes the door and me and Niall walk off and goes inside and order**20 minutes later**I pay the food and Niall grabs it as we walk back to the car.

Y/N’s P.O.V

I understood Harry’s wishes so I stayed in the car while him and Niall get the food as I’m playing on my phone I got a text my phone, “Hey we’re coming.” I look up and suddenly felt wet and I couldn’t control it..the way he was walking towards the car. A breath left my body, “Jesus..”

summary: I know it's a little late but I so often read that Harry looked so happy at the met gala and I'm kinda like not agreeing. I...
body: I know it’s a little late but I so often read that Harry looked so happy at the met gala and I’m kinda like not agreeing. I believe that ge did those drugs/alcohol because he felt alone and wanted to fit in. Like the story about him on dunkirk set, when he laughed even if he didn’t understand them just to be part if them. Maybe I’m wrong but I thought when he was away from friends he seemed lost and to me this just shows that he’s still our baby and that he needs his baby to guide him

title: Met Ready! (Harry Styles Blurb)
body:
Description: [request] Getting ready for the met with Harry!!

Omg my first Harry fic!! Thank you<3333

 You had never felt so proud of Harry before, he loved fashion. He loved showing the expression through outfits and you adored it about him. He was always showing you new suits he wanted to buy and would ask your opinion about them. So when he was asked to be a host at the Met Gala both of you were over the moon. The Met was such a big thing for Harry, not only was it the biggest fashion event in the industry but it was both of your first times going. 

 An invitation had been extended out to you both last year but your busy schedules got in the way and Harry had been finishing a tour. This year you were excited for the theme, you were excited to see what Harry had chosen to wore as he wanted to keep it a secret and surprise you. 

 ‘’Harry! Babe let me see!’’ You yell to him from the living room. 

You hear your bedroom door open and footsteps down the hall, ‘’Ready?’’ He teases, ‘’Close your eyes!’’ 

 You roll your eyes, ‘’Harry!’’ You whine. 

‘‘Okay, okay.’‘ He steps out from around the corner and your jaw drops in shock, he looked so good! 

‘‘Oh my gosh I love it!’‘ You practically scream walking over to him looking at the details, ‘‘I love the top and how you can see you’re tattoos, it’s simple but perfect!’‘ 

‘‘You really think it’s okay?’‘ He says, he didn’t sound as confident as usual. ‘‘I’m nervous people won’t like it.’‘ 

‘‘Harry people will love it! I promise!’‘ You say trying to reassure him. ‘‘They however won’t like how this is tied,’‘ You say laughing at his attempt to tie the front. 

 He pouts leaning in whispering to you, ‘’I thought it looked weird too,’’ He admits and you smile scrunching your nose, whoever told him that was lying. ‘’Can you fix it?’’

 You smile untying it for him, you watch as he studies your face in full concentration. You bite your bottom lip trying to make sure it looked perfect, ‘’You look beautiful by the way,’’ He says making you smile. 

 You look up at him through your lashes slightly blushing, it was crazy after all this time he still had that effect on you. ‘’There!’’ You say to him satisfied with how it turned out. He walks over to the mirror taking a glance at it and turns around and smiles to you. ‘’Look good?’’ You ask him. 

‘‘Yes, thank you!’‘ He says leaning in kissing you, when he pulls back you laugh noticing the lipstick stain now on his lips. You take your hand trying to wipe the remains away, ‘‘Sorry couldn’t help it!’‘ He says smiling mischievously at you. 

 ‘’Wait a minute,’’ you say glancing at his ear, ‘’Is that my earring?’’
